title: JUANITA JOAN MORRISON GILL
maintext: JUANITA JOAN MORRISON GILL, 87, of Salt Rock, died Jan. 27. Funeral service will be 1 p.m. Thursday at Wallace Funeral Home and Chapel, Barboursville; burial at Gill Cemetery. Visitation will be 6-8 p.m. Wednesday at the funeral home. www.timeformemory.com/wallace
